precis:
Amendments to the ALBERTA FISHERY REGULATIONS exempting freshwater shrimp
from the application of the Regulations, clarifying restrictions on the
use of fish for bait, restricting the possession of live game fish, and
inserting a close time that was inadvertently omitted.
